<item>
            <title>[LU-5191] Parallel-scale has script error for ZFS</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5191</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Appears to be a basic Bash error:&lt;br/&gt;
/usr/lib64/lustre/tests/parallel-scale.sh: line 138: &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;: missing `&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&apos;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Test returns garbage for summary (-nan) - not sure if the failure is related, as I shift to a different version of lustre/tests to complete my runs&lt;br/&gt;
Line is question is:&lt;br/&gt;
(code)&lt;br/&gt;
[ $(facet_fstype $SINGLEMDS) = zfs -o $(facet_fstype &quot;ost1&quot;) = zfs] &amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;br/&gt;
        SLOW=$ZFSSLOW&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(code)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
